de.sogomn.engine

Class Screen

  • java.lang.Object
    • de.sogomn.engine.Screen

  • public final class Screen
extends java.lang.Object
    This class represents a screen. Uses a JFrame internally which holds the content and can be shown with the show() method.
    Author:
    Sogomn
